<head>SKEPTICISM</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">懷疑主義</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>DOCTRINE that one SHOULD DOUBT AND CONTINUE TO INVESTIGATE EVERYTHING.</p>
    </div>
